# Project Overview

Full-stack monorepo with separate deployments and a shared database.

| Directory | Stack | Purpose |
|-----------|-------|---------|
| `src/api/` | Python / FastAPI | Backend API |
| `src/frontend/` | Angular 18 | Frontend application |
| `e2e/` | Playwright | End-to-end tests |
| `docs/` | Diataxis | Business & technical documentation |
| `tools/` | TypeScript | Dev utilities, MCP servers |

## Before Answering Any Question

1. Read the relevant `ai-context.md` in the project directory
2. Check `docs/3-reference/meta/AI_CONTEXT.md` for documentation navigation
3. Follow project-specific rules in `.cursor/rules/`

## Git Workflow

**Branch format:** `<prefix>/PROJ-XXX-short-description`

**Prefixes:** `feat`, `fix`, `hotfix`, `refactor`, `chore`, `docs`, `test`

**Commit format** (Conventional Commits):
```
feat(PROJ-123): add user authentication
fix(PROJ-456): resolve API timeout
```

## Code Quality

- **Python**: ruff (lint + format), mypy (strict), pre-commit hooks
- **Angular**: ESLint + Stylelint via `yarn lint`
- **SQL**: sqlfluff
- Run tests before committing — pre-commit hooks enforce this
